953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T17:11:23.000Z","msg":"你試下搵啲cafe仔，in就in樓面先，但係問下老細可唔可以入水吧學下野。我有朋友係零經驗，佢都係咁做。最後由樓面轉咗做水吧。"},{"pid":"294ab26231bfe832c1707941f7ed6cda632156dd","tid":270954,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T18:09:41.000Z","msg":"mc cafe"},{"pid":"565ca6f31d0357114ee85705b73de570223f9dff","tid":270954,"uid":68490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T03:38:55.000Z","msg":"最尾去左in pcc<br />\n有無人最近都in左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f710925c959e052e16c652b98687dcde8de5ae5","tid":270954,"uid":78839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T05:11:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最尾去左in pcc<br />\n有無人最近都in左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想去in 問你啲咩呀巴打"},{"pid":"0bbab415f82dfae812e794bfad53360f90dd515e","tid":270954,"uid":68490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T10:03:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最尾去左in pcc<br />\n有無人最近都in左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想去in 問你啲咩呀巴打</blockquote><br />\n普通吹下水咋<br />\n問下你點解想入 介紹自己之類"}]}